OL,3,CDavid Lammy becomes first black Lord
OL,4,CChancellor
OL,6,FAddressing Lammy in a speech on
OL,7,FWednesday, Baroness Carr said: "Your
OL,8,Fswearing-in marks the first
OL,9,Fappointment, not before time, of a
OL,10,Fblack lord chancellor and secretary of
OL,11,Fstate for justice."
OL,13,FShe added that she looked forward to
OL,14,Fworking with him, and building a
OL,15,Fstrong relationship.
