OL,3,CDavid Lammy becomes first black Lord
OL,4,CChancellor
OL,6,FIn his speech, Lammy said he was
OL,7,F"incredibly proud to be the first lord
OL,8,Fchancellor of African and Caribbean
OL,9,Fheritage".
OL,11,F"I stand here humbled, I stand here
OL,12,Fhonoured. And believe me when I say, I
OL,13,Fstand here feeling the full weight of
OL,14,Fthis ancient office," he said.
OL,16,FLammy said as a child he could never
OL,17,Fhave imagined being in the position he
OL,18,Fheld today, but that in many ways "it
OL,19,Ffeels like coming home".
