OL,3,CDavid Lammy becomes first black Lord
OL,4,CChancellor
OL,6,FThe Attorney General Richard Hermer KC
OL,7,Fsaid it was his "pleasure" to welcome
OL,8,F"his truly dear friend" as Lord
OL,9,FChancellor, saying that as the first
OL,10,Fblack person to hold the post, he
OL,11,Fwould "inspire countless young people".
OL,13,FHe said that in a "wonderfully diverse
OL,14,Fmulticultural society", anyone could
OL,15,Freach the top, irrespective of the
OL,16,Fcolour of their skin, what god they
OL,17,Fbelieved in, or their financial
OL,18,Fbackground.
